  "texts": [
    "The presence of a human-like personality can enhance the user's ability to derive practical benefits from the system and increase satisfaction by making interactions more enjoyable and engaging.",
    "Thus, this study suggests the following hypotheses: H6a Human-like personality in ChatGPT has a positive impact on utilitarian value derived from it.",
    "H6b Human-like personality in ChatGPT has a positive impact on satisfaction with it.",
    "Utilitarian value is understood as the functional or practical benefits a user obtains from a product or service 60.",
    "It often pertains to increased productivity, efficiency, or improved task performance 61."
  ]
}